'''APM Automation Solutions''' is an [[Israel]]i-based developer of solids volume and level measurement instrumentation established in [[Tel Aviv]], [[Israel]].<ref name="VM">{{cite news | last = | first = | title =Emerson Process Management Acquires APM Automation Solutions | newspaper =| location = | pages = | language = | publisher =''Valve Magazine''| date =31 December 2013 | url =http://www.valvemagazine.com/index.php/industry-headlines/industry-headlines/valve-manufacturing/5571-emerson-process-management-acquires-apm-automation-solutions | accessdate =6 November 2015}}</ref><ref name="DNRPS">{{cite news | last = | first = | title =DNR Process Solutions to distribute level measurement instruments in major Asian countries | newspaper =| location = | pages = | language = | publisher =''dnrps''| date =22 February 2013 | url =http://www.dnrps.com/dnr-process-solutions-to-distribute-level-measurement-instruments-in-major-asian-countries.html | accessdate =6 November 2015}}</ref> The APM technology is used in all the bulk solids industries such as:food and beverage, metals and mining, power, cement, coal, chemical, pulp and paper, and other industries.<ref name="AW">{{cite news | last =Dan | first =Miklovic | title =Linking People, Processes and Technology in APM | newspaper =| location = | pages = | language = | publisher =''Automation World''| date =25 June 2015 | url =http://www.automationworld.com/maintenance-reliability/linking-people-processes-and-technology-apm | accessdate =6 November 2015}}</ref> The outfit recently became part of the [[Emerson Electric|Emerson Process Management business]] under Rosemount Brand.<ref name="vma">{{cite news | last = | first = | title =Emerson Process Management Acquires APM Automation Solutions | newspaper =| location = | pages = | language = | publisher =''VMA''| date =31 December 2013 | url =http://www.vma.org/news/151353/Emerson-Process-Management-Acquires-APM-Automation-Solutions.htm | accessdate =6 November 2015}}</ref><ref name="PIM">{{cite news | last = | first = | title =Emerson Buys Solids {{sic|nolink=y|Measurment}} specialist APM | newspaper =| location = | pages = | language = | publisher =''Process Industry Match''| date = | url =http://www.processindustrymatch.com/materials-news/708-emerson-buys-solids-measurment-specilist-apm | accessdate =6 November 2015}}</ref>
==History== APM Automation Solutions was established in 2005 in Tel Aviv, Israel by Ofir Perl and Yossi Zlotnick. After the acquisition, Ofir Perl became the GM in Rosemount Analytical under Emerson Process Management. Yossi Zlotnick was also a co-founder of the firm. He is the CTO in the APM site under the Rosemount Level team. The co-founders have been involved in managing and leading large-scale development projects in telecommunications and signal processing fields for many years.<ref name="GL">{{cite news|last=Shiri Habib |first=Valdhorn |title=Emerson buys Israel's APM Automation Solutions |newspaper= |location= |pages= |language= |publisher=''Globes'' |date=19 December 2013 |url=http://www.globes.co.il/en/article-1000903149 |accessdate=6 November 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305014439/http://www.globes.co.il/en/article-1000903149 |archivedate=5 March 2016 }}</ref>
APM Automation Solutions has set a network of global distributors/agents that supply its products in over 30 countries across the US, [[Europe]] and [[Asia-Pacific]].<ref name="DNRPS"/> In December 18, 2013, APM Automation Solutions was acquired by Emerson Process Management. By this acquisition, Emerson expands its capabilities in solids measurement applications. Emerson operates in 150 countries and has a market cap of $48.1&nbsp;billion on the [[New York Stock Exchange]] with annual sales of $24.4&nbsp;billion.<ref name="GL"/><ref name="CD">{{cite news | last = | first = | title =Emerson Acquires APM Automation Solutions | newspaper =| location = | pages = | language = | publisher =''Control Design''| date =7 January 2013 | url =http://www.controldesign.com/industrynews/2014/emerson-acquires-apm-automation-solutions/ | accessdate =6 November 2015}}</ref><ref name="EP">{{cite news | last = | first = | title =Emerson acquires APM Automation Solutions | newspaper =| location = | pages = | language = | publisher =''Emerson Process''| date = | url =http://www2.emersonprocess.com/en-us/news/pr/pages/1312-apm.aspx | accessdate =6 November 2015}}</ref><ref name="PENG">{{cite news | last =Brian | first =Tinham | title =Emerson acquires APM Automation Solutions for solid improvement | newspaper =| location = | pages = | language = | publisher =''Plant Engineer''| date =20 December 2013 | url =http://www.plantengineer.org.uk/plant-engineer-news/emerson-acquires-apm-automation-solutions-for-solid-improvement/58589 | accessdate =6 November 2015}}</ref>
==Products and services== APM Automation Solutions is a manufacturer of volume and level measurement instrumentation. The company offers [[Photoacoustic imaging|acoustic imaging]] and [[3D projection|3D mapping]] technologies e.g. the 3DLevelScanner. These technologies are "meant to take the guesswork out of measuring the level, volume and mass of bulk solids and powders" stored inside a silo or open bin. These have found applications in food & beverage, metals and mining, power, chemical production, cement, coal, pulp and paper, and other industries.<ref name="DNRPS"/><ref name="AU">{{cite news | last = | first = | title =Emerson acquires APM Automation Solutions | newspaper =| location = | pages = | language = | publisher =''Automation''| date = | url =http://www.automation.com/automation-news/industry/emerson-acquires-apm-automation-solutions | accessdate =6 November 2015}}</ref><ref name="COM">{{cite news | last = | first = | title =JK Vine Consulting Joins the Compuware APM Accelerate Partner Program | newspaper =| location = | pages = | language = | publisher =''Compuware''| date =16 June 2014 | url =http://www.cmo.com.au/mediareleases/19633/jk-vine-consulting-joins-the-compuware-apm/ | accessdate =6 November 2015}}</ref>
